rows.label: qst201501_msg0001
rows.name: Ugh... Not my lucky day.

rows.label: qst201501_msg0002
rows.name: What's wrong?

rows.label: qst201501_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh, nothing much. Only managed
to sink my bloody ship!

rows.label: qst201501_msg0004
rows.name:
My crew are safe and sound, but my
cargo? Probably lying at the bottom
of the Cloud Sea by now.

rows.label: qst201501_msg0005
rows.name: Now I'm up a creek without a paddle...

rows.label: qst201501_msg0006
rows.name: That's awful...

rows.label: qst201501_msg0007
rows.name:
This ship of yours... It was carrying
Gulan cargo, am I right?

rows.label: qst201501_msg0008
rows.name: You...you're the witch!

rows.label: qst201501_msg0009
rows.name:
Some of my crew said they saw
a witch in the distance as the ship
was sinking, but I never thought...

rows.label: qst201501_msg0010
rows.name: Oh no...

rows.label: qst201501_msg0011
rows.name: Screw the plan! I'm gettin' outta here!

rows.label: qst201501_msg0012
rows.name: Ah, wait...!

rows.label: qst201501_msg0013
rows.name: A speedy fellow, isn't he?

rows.label: qst201501_msg0014
rows.name: What was all that about?

rows.label: qst201501_msg0015
rows.name:
Running away at the sight of
someone's face. How rude.

rows.label: qst201501_msg0016
rows.name:
Azami, you seem to know about this
sunken ship business. Could you
enlighten us?

rows.label: qst201501_msg0017
rows.name:
But of course. It was all a part of my
recon mission.

rows.label: qst201501_msg0018
rows.name:
So you would also know the reason
why it sank?

rows.label: qst201501_msg0019
rows.name:
Ahaha, naturally! Because I was the
one who sank it!

rows.label: qst201501_msg0020
rows.name: You sank it?! But why?

rows.label: qst201501_msg0021
rows.name: Oh, come on, it's not such a big deal.

rows.label: qst201501_msg0022
rows.name:
They were behaving so openly
suspicious. Clearly shipping cargo
of a dubious nature.

rows.label: qst201501_msg0023
rows.name:
Sinking their ship seemed the sensible
course of action. It put an end to their
mischief and lightened my workload.

rows.label: qst201501_msg0024
rows.name:
Even so, that seems to be going a little
overboard...

rows.label: qst201501_msg0025
rows.name: I was lonely! Can you blame me?

rows.label: qst201501_msg0026
rows.name:
Lonely? You sunk their ship because
you were lonely?!

rows.label: qst201501_msg0027
rows.name:
Now don't give me that. You know
I'm just dying to be with my beloved
Driver...

rows.label: qst201501_msg0028
rows.name:
Can't you try to see things from my
perspective?

rows.label: qst201501_msg0029
rows.name:
Besides, I never wanted to be doing
recon in the first place...

rows.label: qst201501_msg0030
rows.name:
There should have been someone
to keep me company!

rows.label: qst201501_msg0031
rows.name: I get lonely very easily, you know...

rows.label: qst201501_msg0032
rows.name: Still...

rows.label: qst201501_msg0033
rows.name:
Actually, I can sort of see where
she's coming from...

rows.label: qst201501_msg0034
rows.name:
Maybe we could accompany her
on her mission?

rows.label: qst201501_msg0035
rows.name: Oh? My darling Driver will join me?

rows.label: qst201501_msg0036
rows.name:
Then I'll be a good girl from now on.
I'll do as I'm told.

rows.label: qst201501_msg0037
rows.name: Meleph? What do you want to do?

rows.label: qst201501_msg0038
rows.name:
Hmm. Well, I'd rather this than have
her running out of control.

rows.label: qst201501_msg0039
rows.name: So you'll join me?! Oh, this is perfect!

rows.label: qst201501_msg0040
rows.name:
All right, I'll get straight back to
surveillance duty.

rows.label: qst201501_msg0041
rows.name: Off we go to the Great Blowhole!
